[{"content":"Introduction On March 11th, the documentary \u0026ldquo;Guarding Liberation West 3\u0026rdquo;, co-produced by the Changsha Public Security Bureau and Bilibili, came to a successful conclusion, amassing over 200 million views and sparking heated discussions. Throughout the series, it featured both bizarre incidents that left viewers laughing and crying, as well as thrilling on-site arrests, showcasing both the stern and rigorous law enforcement procedures and heartwarming grassroots services. Behind the hustle and bustle, the guardians never rest; in recent years, documentaries focusing on law enforcement have increasingly attracted the younger generation. Today, let us take a step into these \u0026ldquo;outposts\u0026rdquo; that serve and protect the people, gaining an understanding of the most authentic front lines of police work.\nGuarding Liberation West The \u0026ldquo;Guarding Liberation West\u0026rdquo; series is a legal education documentary centered around the daily work of police officers in Changsha, Hunan Province. This documentary deeply showcases the routine tasks of urban police officers in the central business district of a metropolis, revealing the intricate interplay of law, reason, emotion, and reality within complex policing situations through activities such as police patrols, multi-departmental cooperation, suspect interrogations, and involvement in major cases. It portrays a vivid image of responsible, rational, and compassionate police officers, and disseminates relevant safety and legal knowledge to the public through various case stories. The featured police officers in the show have distinct characteristics, each with their own areas of expertise and endearing personalities, which constitutes one of the main attractions of \u0026ldquo;Guarding Liberation West\u0026rdquo;.\nThanks to the rich experience of Hunan TV in producing variety shows, and due to the everyday, relatable nature of the cases depicted in \u0026ldquo;Guarding Liberation West\u0026rdquo;, the program infuses a certain level of entertainment into the rigorous process of law enforcement, ensuring seriousness while also catering to viewers\u0026rsquo; preferences for amusement. In the bar and commercial districts, an abundance of civil disturbances resulting from alcohol consumption serve as a recurring thread throughout the three episodes. Incidents under the influence of alcohol can sometimes jeopardize public safety, create misunderstandings, appear absurdly comical, or lead to tragedies. The show captures life\u0026rsquo;s nuances vividly in minor incidents while maintaining strict rigor in significant matters, providing viewers with a delightful viewing experience.\n\u0026ldquo;Guarding Liberation West\u0026rdquo; is filled with wit, humor, and laugh-out-loud moments, telling stories of human life and its vicissitudes in the Liberation West area of Changsha, portraying the spirit, unique personalities, and selfless dedication of grassroots police officers in the new era. While conducting serious legal education, it also offers a sense of relaxation and enjoyment, making it an essential companion during meals.\nBig City, No Small Matters \u0026ldquo;Big City, No Small Matters\u0026rdquo; is a police documentary produced by Oriental Satellite TV. Unlike \u0026ldquo;Guarding Liberation West\u0026rdquo;, this program shifts its focus from grassroots police station affairs to the actions against crime, concentrating on criminal and economic cases in Shanghai (referred to as \u0026ldquo;Shen City\u0026rdquo;). The show embeds itself within various criminal investigation and economic investigation teams across Shanghai, closely following the processes of solving cases involving forensic science, anti-theft, anti-fraud, plainclothes operations, major cases, and drug enforcement. Viewers can experience the intensity firsthand through the lens, accompanying law enforcement officers to the front lines of capturing suspects, immersively feeling the tense atmosphere and recreating the thrilling moments of apprehension.\nCriminal and economic crimes are more serious and hardcore compared to civil cases. This series covers not only recurring heinous acts such as drug trafficking and tax evasion but also new forms of crime like online and telecommunications fraud. The show particularly highlights these novel criminal methods, serving as a stark reminder that \u0026ldquo;the law\u0026rsquo;s net is vast and though it may have gaps, none can escape.\u0026rdquo; It further embodies the professional attitude of investigative teams who constantly monitor and vigilantly protect society. A thought-provoking aspect is that a significant number of suspects involved in online fraud are young people adept at internet technology, yet often lack knowledge about relevant laws, only realizing they\u0026rsquo;ve broken the law upon arrest. This underscores the importance of economic legal education. Concurrently, elderly individuals are more susceptible to falling victim to online scams, making it an urgent social development issue to integrate this demographic into an increasingly digital payment-dominated environment.\nIf you\u0026rsquo;re drawn to the hardcore elements of criminal and economic investigations, eager to explore the strategies behind cracking major cases, or simply wish to experience the adrenaline rush of frontline law enforcement, \u0026ldquo;Big City, No Small Matters\u0026rsquo; might just be the perfect fit for you.\nForensic Files \u0026ldquo;Forensic Files\u0026rdquo; is a police documentary produced by China Central Television, which uses a series of classic cases as a vehicle to narrate the entire process of case investigation from the perspective of forensic experts, tightly integrating criminalistics with detective work. Although the program mainly tells the story through the eyes of forensic experts, it presents a comprehensive view of all stages from identification to apprehension, featuring a tight pace and interlocking clues and motives, creating a strong sense of deduction that is both suspenseful and captivating.\nThe show particularly highlights the forensic criminal investigation techniques, which are highly specialized and core content. For instance, regarding the concept of time of death, \u0026ldquo;Forensic Files\u0026rdquo; provides detailed explanations: how forensic experts use specific methods to accurately estimate the time of death for victims, thereby providing solid evidence for detectives to solve cases.\nUnder the scalpel, the last words of the victims are conveyed; under the microscope, the wrongdoings of criminals are exposed. \u0026ldquo;Forensic Files\u0026rdquo; guides viewers to unravel the intricate details of cases, revealing all hidden truths. While solving cases, the program also conveys the noble professional spirit of forensic experts, who speak for the deceased and advocate for the rights of the living.\nObserving the dynamics of society, safeguarding local tranquility. Grassroots police officers, criminal investigation officers, and economic crime investigation officers jointly maintain the peace of the city, piecing together the truth like a puzzle, breaking through barriers amidst confusion to pinpoint the source of evil. You may rarely encounter them, but more often than not, they blend into the hustle and bustle of urban life and the everyday routines of the marketplace. In times of urgent police situations, they are the brave ones going against the tide; after the storm has passed, they shine as the most dazzling light in the sky above the city. Their brilliance may be hidden in the ordinary, yet their true colors still shine through even in understated ways.\n引入 3月11日，长沙市公安局联合哔哩哔哩制作的纪录片《守护解放西3》圆满完结，本片狂揽两亿播放，引发热烈讨论。在系列纪录片中，既有让人哭笑不得的“奇葩”事件，也有惊心动魄的现场抓捕，既展现了冷峻严肃的执法过程，也记录了温暖感人的基层服务。 在繁华背后，守护永不打烊，近些年来，警务题材的纪录片越来越吸引着年轻一代。今天，就让我们一起来走进这些便民护民的“哨站”，了解最真实的警情第一线。\n守护解放西 《守护解放西》系列是一部以湖南长沙市民警办案为核心内容的普法纪录片。这部纪录片深度展示了大都市核心商圈城市警察的日常工作，通过民警巡逻、多警种联动、疑犯审讯、要案参与等事件，展现警情复杂地带的法、理、情、事，展现有担当、有理性、有人情的人民警察形象，并通过各类案件故事普及相关安全和法律常识。参与出镜的警员特点鲜明，在工作上各有擅长领域，在性格上各有可爱之处，这也是解放西的一大看点。\n得益于湖南台综艺制作的丰富经验，也由于解放西涉及的案件比较日常化、生活化，《守护解放西》给严谨认真的执法过程融入了一定的娱乐元素，确保普法节目的严肃性的同时，兼顾了观众喜闻乐见的趣味性。在酒馆商区，酒后滋事的民事警情极其丰富，成为贯穿三集的重要线索之一。酒精催化之下发生的事情，有时危害公共安全，有时导致误会频出，有时显得荒唐可笑，有时甚至造成悲剧。节目制作时，在小事上表现生动，在大事上保持严谨，给观众提供了舒适的观片体验。\n《守护解放西》有梗有趣有笑点，讲述发生在长沙解放西地带的种种人间烟火的故事，展现新时代基层民警的精神风貌、特色个性以及忘我精神。在严肃普法的过程中也给人心情上的放松，绝对是下饭必备。\n大城无小事 《大城无小事》是东方卫视的警务纪录片。不同于《守护解放西》，节目将视线从基层派出所事务转向了打击犯罪的行动，集中聚焦申城的刑事、经济类案件，蹲点驻守上海市各刑侦、经侦队伍，深入刑事科学、反侵财、反诈、便衣、重案、缉毒等侦查队伍，全程跟拍破案过程。观众可以通过镜头随民警奔赴抓捕嫌犯的第一现场，深临其境感受紧张氛围，还原惊险抓捕时刻。\n刑事、经济类犯罪相较民事案件更加地严肃、硬核，节选案件既包括贩毒、逃税等老生常谈的恶行事件，也包括了网络电信诈骗等新型犯罪方式。节目聚焦于更多新型犯罪方式，警示着心怀不轨之人“法网恢恢，疏而不漏”，更体现着侦查队伍动态监测、时刻守护的职业态度。引人深思的是，相当部分的实施网络诈骗的嫌疑人是对网络技术更加擅长的年轻人，而他们往往对相关法律疏于认识，遭到逮捕时才惊觉触犯了法律，更加体现出经济普法的重要性。同时，容易收到网络诈骗的受害者又是中老年人群，让中老年人群融入线上支付占主流的大环境，也成为社会发展亟需解决的问题。\n如果喜欢硬核的刑侦、经侦过程，窥探大案背后的破解之法，或者希望体验一线抓捕的紧张刺激，这部《大城无小事》也许会适合你。\n法医密档 《法医密档》是中央电视台出品的警务记录片。节目以一个个经典案例为载体，从法医的视角讲述案件侦破的过程，将刑事科学技术与刑侦紧密结合。虽然是从法医的视角讲述案件，但是节目从鉴定到抓捕各个过程全面展现、节奏紧凑，线索、动机环环相扣，颇具推理感，紧张而精彩。\n节目着重介绍法医的刑事调查技术，十分硬核。例如死亡时间的概念，《法医密档》中就会对死亡时间做详细的介绍：法医是通过什么方式，能够精准的推算出死者的死亡时间，进而为刑侦人员提供可靠的破案依据。除了“死亡时间”之外，还有如何确定“死者身份”、如何通过一滴干枯的血迹寻找凶手等等。\n手术刀下传达着被害者的遗言，显微镜上揭露了犯罪者的恶行，《法医密档》将会带你在案件的蛛丝马迹里抽丝剥茧，找出一切未知的真相。在破解案件的同时，也在传递法医“为死者代言，为生者谋权”的职业精神。\n察一态社会，守一方安宁。基层民警、刑侦民警、经侦民警，共同守望着城市的一方安宁，如拼图般还原出事件真相，在扑朔迷离中刺破壁垒，去锁定邪恶的源头。或许你很少会遇见他们，更多的时候，他们隐入都市的喧闹，隐入市井烟火的日常。警情险急时，他们是站在风口浪尖的逆行者，雨过天晴，他们是这座城市上空最耀眼的光芒。光华隐于平凡，淡彩亦显本色。\n图片 “Guarding Liberation West” “Forensic Files” “Guarding Liberation West” “Big City, No Small Matters” ","date":"2022-03-24T00:00:00Z","image":"http://localhost:1313/2022/the-cold-and-warmth-of-the-police-station/t019aad1f5548ec9421_hu8e26b2051a5a96b9128394306a827e9c_280494_120x120_fill_box_smart1_3.png","permalink":"http://localhost:1313/2022/the-cold-and-warmth-of-the-police-station/","title":"The Cold and Warmth of the Police Station"},{"content":"This article offers a sample of basic Markdown syntax t